To chat about Tails:

1. Boot Tails.
2. Clic on the Pidgin icon (third on the right of System) or through the menu *Applications* → *Internet* → *Pidgin*.
3. Wait until Pidgin is connected. Once this is done, Pidgin window will be populated with `#tails` and `#tor`.
4. Double-clic on `#tails`.
5. Select the `#tails` tab that has opened in the chat window.

To use OTR on top of the preconfigured IRC account:

1. Double-clic on the right nick in the list at the right of the chat window.
2. In the new tab, use the menu OTR and select *Start private conversation*.
3. Verify your peer identity using *Authenticate buddy* option in the same menu.
